Text:
Di Dewan Negara menjawab soalan Datuk Haji Bashir bin Haji Alias minta @mafimalaysia menyatakan apakah mekanisme bagi mengatasi masalah rantaian bekalan makanan ke Labuan yang mengakibatkan kekurangan bekalan makanan dan kenaikan mendadak harga barangan.
https://t.co/SVQdTuvL3o
Translated_Tweets:
The House of Representatives answered Datuk Haji Bashir bin Haji Alias ​​asking @Mafimalaysia to state what the mechanism was to overcome the problem of food supply chains to Labuan which led to a shortage of food supply and the sharp rise in prices of goods.
https://t.co/svqdtuvl3o

Text:
Patutlah @rafiziramli ckp serampang dua mata.

Selain dpt atasi kekurangan bekalan makanan, dpt bantu tingkatkan pendapatan golongan B40.

B40 dpt pendapatan tambahan. ✅️
Bekalan makanan dpt ditingkatkan. ✅️

Kill two birds with one stone. Harap² program ni berhasil.
Translated_Tweets:
It should be @rafiziramli ckp for two eyes.

In addition to being able to overcome the shortage of food supply, it can help increase the income of the B40.

B40 can be additional income. ✅️
Food supply can be improved. ✅️

Kill two birds with one stone. Hope this program works.
